{"Sid":0,"Did":18011,"Id":"282324","Title":"頭城忠孝新村天后宮呂祖大仙神像","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/object/2020-02-24/de812ac9-6ecd-4a35-9c08-4dc121482062/collection/14ad119c-414d-4593-9e68-22a13f39f01b/108-her-cw-1154-201910252239505db2e16a5063c0.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Object","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n呂祖大仙，即一般所稱之「呂洞賓」，原名呂喦，道號純陽子，為道教著名仙者，經常被與其他神明並稱，如八仙、五恩主或五文昌等；也是多種行業之守護神，如理髮、礦業或淘金等，但也具醫神、武神、科考神或財神的特質。 　　大陳島雖無主祀呂祖大仙之廟宇，但轉進來台之後，許多大陳移民聚落廟宇均以呂祖大仙為陪祀神，顯得相當特別。頭城忠孝新村天后宮主神為媽祖，其龍邊神龕奉祀呂祖大仙，其神像乃是居民在大陳撤退時，自下大陳大沙頭娘娘廟揹負來台奉祀，為等身軟身神像，相當罕見。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.886634","Keyword_Latitude":"24.935827","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/object/27759F77-5F4D-4084-AE2A-38EDB3B9A378","Original_Identifier":"282324","Keyword_Subject_1":"民俗與宗教","alias":"","alternativeHeadline":"","Keywords":"大陳 / 天后宮 / 呂祖大仙 / 忠孝新村 / 神像 / 頭城","dates":"創作時間 / 民國/戰後時期","LastUpdateTime":"2020/02/24 19:46:58","Creator":"不詳","publisher":"","mediaType":"有形文物","language":"","timelines":"","city":"宜蘭縣頭城鎮","address":"忠孝新村54號","lng":"121.886634","lat":"24.935827","contributors":"","contributor":"林世傑/ 蔡明志","size":"","admin":"","award":"","character":"","contentLocation":"","acquireWay":"","acquireSource":"","storage":"","version":"","isbn":"","onlineAuthLink":"","stuff":"","url":"","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","citation":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/object/2020-02-24/de812ac9-6ecd-4a35-9c08-4dc121482062/collectionOpen/5313d199-c59c-46e4-9b18-29b3ea7c8fe2/108-her-cw-1154-re-201910252241445db2e16a5063c0.jpg"}}